<section class="intro-statement space">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-0 text-center">
        <p class="intro-accent" data-ani="fadein"><em>Locally Owned, Sea-Tested Since 2009</em></p>
        <h2 class="intro-heading" data-ani="slideinup" data-ani-delay="0.1">Real People, Real Boats, Real Rhodes</h2>
        <p class="intro-body" data-ani="fadein" data-ani-delay="0.25">
          We are not a booking platform. We are a family of sailors, skippers, and sea lovers based right here in Rhodes. When you reach out to us, you speak directly with people who have spent their lives on this water. Whether you want a quiet afternoon exploring hidden coves on your own, or a full-day cruise with friends, we will help you find exactly the right experience — with honest advice and no pressure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro-statement {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .intro-accent {
    font-family: var(--style-font, 'Cormorant Garamond', serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--theme-color, #1CA8CB);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .intro-heading {
    font-family: var(--title-font, 'Manrope', sans-serif);
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--title-color, #1a1a2b);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .intro-body {
    font-family: var(--body-font, 'Inter', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #6e7070;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .intro-heading {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
